OL,3,CWhen will the election results in your
OL,4,Carea be announced?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer, Kieran
OL,7,FCarter
OL,9,FThe country headed to the polls on
OL,10,FThursday to vote in local and mayoral
OL,11,Felections across England, as well as
OL,12,Felections for the devolved parliaments
OL,13,Fof Scotland and Wales.
OL,15,FUnlike in general elections, results
OL,16,Fwon't be counted as quickly, with only
OL,17,Fa third of authorities doing so
OL,18,Fovernight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778324573
OL,3,CWhen will the election results in your
OL,4,Carea be announced?
OL,6,FNearly 5,000 council seats are up for
OL,7,Felection across 136 councils in
OL,8,FEngland.
OL,10,FUnder a new voting system, Wales will
OL,11,Felect 96 members of its Senedd, up
OL,12,Ffrom 60 in previous years.
OL,14,FScotland will elect all 129 of its
OL,15,FMSPs in Holyrood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778324573
OL,3,CWhen will the election results in your
OL,4,Carea be announced?
OL,6,FThe first results are expected around
OL,7,F1 am on Friday, with Broxbourne and
OL,8,FHalton hoping to be the first to
OL,9,Fdeclare, though all times are
OL,10,Festimated and various factors, such as
OL,11,Frecounts or turnout, could affect
OL,12,Factual declaration times.
OL,14,FWales is also electing representatives
OL,15,Funder an entirely new system with a
OL,16,Freduced number of constituencies,
OL,17,Fmaking declaration times more likely
OL,18,Fto differ from what is expected.
OL,20,FFour councils expect to declare their
OL,21,Fresults on Saturday instead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
