OL,4,Carea be announced?
OL,6,FFor the first time in Wales, voters
OL,7,Fwill vote for a party, not an
OL,8,Findividual candidate, with the winning
OL,9,FMSs being elected based on the
OL,10,Fproportion of votes each party
OL,11,Freceives.
OL,13,FAll results are expected to be
OL,14,Fannounced on Friday.
